============================================================
CONFIG REQUIREMENTS
============================================================

Update root `.env.example`:

CRYPTO_FABRIC_ENABLED=true
CRYPTO_FABRIC_MODE=mock
CRYPTO_FABRIC_DRY_RUN=true
CRYPTO_FABRIC_FAIL_CLOSED=true

KEY_REGISTRY_ENABLED=true
KEY_CUSTODY_PROVIDER=mock
KEY_CUSTODY_DRY_RUN=true
KEY_ROTATION_METADATA_ENABLED=true

SIGNING_POLICY_ENABLED=true
SIGNING_PROVIDER=mock
SIGNING_DRY_RUN=true
SIGNING_REQUIRE_APPROVAL=true
SIGNING_DEFAULT_ALGORITHM=mock-ed25519

VERIFICATION_POLICY_ENABLED=true
VERIFICATION_FAIL_CLOSED=true
SIGNED_ENVELOPES_ENABLED=true
SIGNED_ENVELOPE_SUMMARY_ONLY=true

CRYPTO_AUDIT_ENABLED=true
AUDIT_INTEGRITY_CHECK_ENABLED=true
AUDIT_HASH_CHAIN_ENABLED=true

CONFIDENTIAL_COMPUTE_ENABLED=true
CONFIDENTIAL_COMPUTE_MODE=readiness
CONFIDENTIAL_COMPUTE_DRY_RUN=true
TEE_ATTESTATION_ENABLED=true
TEE_ATTESTATION_PROVIDER=mock
TEE_ATTESTATION_DRY_RUN=true

WORKLOAD_CONFIDENTIALITY_PROFILES_ENABLED=true
CONFIDENTIAL_JOBS_ENABLED=true
CONFIDENTIAL_JOBS_DRY_RUN=true

ENCRYPTED_EVIDENCE_VAULT_ENABLED=true
EVIDENCE_VAULT_PROVIDER=mock
EVIDENCE_VAULT_DRY_RUN=true
EVIDENCE_VAULT_EXCLUDE_SECRETS=true

ZK_READINESS_ENABLED=true
ZK_PROOF_PROVIDER=mock
ZK_PROOF_DRY_RUN=true

VERIFIABLE_AGENTS_ENABLED=true
AGENT_IDENTITY_REGISTRY_ENABLED=true
AGENT_COUNCIL_ENABLED=true
AGENT_QUORUM_ENABLED=true
AGENT_QUORUM_REQUIRE_HUMAN_APPROVAL=true
AGENT_QUORUM_MIN_APPROVALS=2

AGENT_DECISION_PROOFS_ENABLED=true
POLICY_PROOFS_ENABLED=true
CONTROL_PROOFS_ENABLED=true
GOVERNANCE_PROOFS_ENABLED=true
RELEASE_GATE_PROOFS_ENABLED=true

Rules:
- Mock providers must work without secrets.
- Real signing, KMS, TEE, vault, or proof providers require explicit config.
- No raw keys may be logged or returned.
- Signed envelopes contain summaries only.
- Verification fails closed when configured.
- Confidential compute is readiness-only by default.
- Agent quorum never replaces human approval for sensitive actions.
- Release gates cannot pass if safety, provenance, or attestation state is unknown.

