============================================================
API RESPONSE FORMAT
============================================================

All endpoints must use standard response shape:

Success:

{
  "ok": true,
  "data": {},
  "error": null,
  "timestamp": "ISO_DATE"
}

Error:

{
  "ok": false,
  "data": null,
  "error": {
    "code": "ERROR_CODE",
    "message": "Human readable message"
  },
  "timestamp": "ISO_DATE"
}

Required error codes:

- CRYPTO_FABRIC_DISABLED
- KEY_RECORD_NOT_FOUND
- KEY_REF_INVALID
- KEY_REVOKED
- SIGNING_POLICY_NOT_FOUND
- VERIFICATION_POLICY_NOT_FOUND
- SIGNING_NOT_CONFIGURED
- SIGNATURE_VERIFICATION_FAILED
- SIGNED_ENVELOPE_NOT_FOUND
- CRYPTO_INTEGRITY_FAILED
- CONFIDENTIAL_COMPUTE_DISABLED
- ENCLAVE_NOT_FOUND
- TEE_ATTESTATION_FAILED
- WORKLOAD_PROFILE_NOT_FOUND
- CONFIDENTIAL_JOB_NOT_FOUND
- CONFIDENTIAL_JOB_BLOCKED
- EVIDENCE_VAULT_RECORD_NOT_FOUND
- ZK_READINESS_ONLY
- VERIFIABLE_AGENTS_DISABLED
- AGENT_IDENTITY_NOT_FOUND
- AGENT_IDENTITY_REVOKED
- AGENT_COUNCIL_NOT_FOUND
- QUORUM_DECISION_NOT_FOUND
- QUORUM_HUMAN_APPROVAL_REQUIRED
- PROOF_NOT_FOUND
- RELEASE_GATE_BLOCKED
- TENANT_ACCESS_DENIED

