- No secrets are exposed.
- DRY_RUN remains true by default.
- Social posting remains approval-gated.
- IoT real actions remain blocked by default.
- Live trading remains blocked by default.
- Cryptographic providers remain mock/dry-run by default.
- Confidential compute remains readiness-only by default.
- README includes Phase 22 documentation.

